  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cute and approachable turn-based deck builder/card battler that combines the battle systems from Tetra Master/Triple Triad and Pokémon. Collect, upgrade, and customize your party to strategically defeat your opponents and save them from the attack on Hex Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/e9931d70109f5855713056b071e56a44.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your arrows to capture the opponent's tokens and convert them into your color. The player with the most tokens in their color at the end of the match wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When arrows connect, a battle is triggered and dice are rolled. Battles may add risk, but allow for additional captures through combos. Element types are vital to your success, and will provide an attack boost when used against weaker elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a87f30d770a7ea0eb473d5e725ef93d8.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/0e764da3e916416a84c8a2745c313e21.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/0e764da3e916416a84c8a2745c313e21.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/0e764da3e916416a84c8a2745c313e21.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover different ways to outwit your opponent and secure the win. Some tokens contain Special Abilities, each with its own unique effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/10198d06a4a30192f8b0004854a9f21d.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/10198d06a4a30192f8b0004854a9f21d.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/10198d06a4a30192f8b0004854a9f21d.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep an eye out for Walls, Field Elements, Bombs, and other obstacles found on the board that can also be used to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/fd93ea7d8bf8049d5757a5cc2e4c5663.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a64c4298a9e13c6440c2e43e42d45a20.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a64c4298a9e13c6440c2e43e42d45a20.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a64c4298a9e13c6440c2e43e42d45a20.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your collection of tokens and critters by looting your opponent after a victory, opening booster packs, and finding treasure chests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/59081cb76289c7da38495b29a595b431.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/89dc3c071054f9a7c2d80b0f9330da85.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tokens come in a variety of designs, elements, abilities, and arrow compositions, allowing you to create a unique party that best fits your playstyle. You can also upgrade and modify your tokens in order to have the upper hand during your next match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/5094121ee6490437ec1f027289cb2698.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/d0d81f641f846eef817f71010b7bfe01.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=373 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in friendly exhibition matches against other players, or put your friendship to the test by looting all of their tokens! Customize the board to your advantage, or leave it to chance and adapt your strategy as you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/2fdf0d5d1ef537422d9ffcf18eaacbb5.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/37483364b67d3dbf3dfd570d9dff9bc1.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/25d3e33eb5c151c5d35d3281ab44f000.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/f2db76a3ecc8f0446f16732682cf8964.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord to leave feedback and get updates, and subscribe to our YouTube channel to see what games we're working on next!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cute and approachable turn-based deck builder/card battler that combines the battle systems from Tetra Master/Triple Triad and Pokémon. Collect, upgrade, and customize your party to strategically defeat your opponents and save them from the attack on Hex Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/e9931d70109f5855713056b071e56a44.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.poster.avif?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.webm?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/487ca48260ca38371698d50a637b65e8.mp4?t=1762799234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your arrows to capture the opponent's tokens and convert them into your color. The player with the most tokens in their color at the end of the match wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When arrows connect, a battle is triggered and dice are rolled. Battles may add risk, but allow for additional captures through combos. Element types are vital to your success, and will provide an attack boost when used against weaker elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305380/extras/a87f30d770a7ea0eb473d5e725ef93d8.webp?t=1762799234\" width=600 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shar